                <mxCell id="notes_bg" value="WORKFLOW NOTES" style="swimlane;startSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#aaaaaa;strokeWidth=1;fontStyle=1;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="490" y="1440" width="720" height="350" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="notes_text" value="&lt;b&gt;Workflow I — Annual Data Snapshot (Batch / Green arrows)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;I.    MCA data pulled: control design attributes, significance of impact, issue mapping&lt;br&gt;II.   Regulatory Inventory pulled: publication tiers and obligation mappings&lt;br&gt;III.  ICAPS open issues pulled and mapped by obligation ID&lt;br&gt;I.a   Business Activity Warehouse metrics pulled (supplemental)&lt;br&gt;D1.  Reconciled snapshot persisted to Snapshot Data Store (data date fixed annually)&lt;br&gt;D2.  Snapshot read by Scoping Service for GAU/publication mapping&lt;br&gt;IV.  Scoped universe handed to Publication Rating Engine&lt;br&gt;V.   100% systemic publication-level IR, CE, and RR ratings calculated and loaded to UI&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Workflow 1 — Assessment Cycle (Primary / Blue arrows)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1.   ICRM Methodology Team opens assessment platform; assigns Business Activity rating&lt;br&gt;2.   Enterprise Compliance Analysts (Preparer) qualify L2/L1 ratings with rationale&lt;br&gt;3.   Business Teams validate source data and submit control evidence&lt;br&gt;4.   Preparer submits assessment; Assessment Service moves status to Pending Approval&lt;br&gt;D3.  Ratings persisted to CRA Assessment DB&lt;br&gt;5.   Approver reviews and approves; status moves to Completed&lt;br&gt;D4.  Aggregation Service reads completed GAU ratings from DB&lt;br&gt;6.   Aggregated risk reports delivered to Senior Management / BRCC&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Workflow A — Reporting and Distribution (Dark Blue arrows)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;A.   Risk ratings sent to GCB Xceptor RPA for downstream automation&lt;br&gt;B.   Ratings and L2 recommendations sent to CIA Monitoring and Testing&lt;br&gt;C.   Aggregated State of Risk report delivered to BRCC and Board of Directors" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=0;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;" parent="notes_bg" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="8" y="26" width="700" height="316" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="meta_bg" value="APPLICATION METADATA" style="swimlane;startSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#aaaaaa;strokeWidth=1;fontStyle=1;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1220" y="1440" width="610" height="350" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="meta_text" value="&lt;b&gt;Application:&lt;/b&gt; Compliance Risk Assessment (CRA)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;CSI ID:&lt;/b&gt; 180236&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Domain:&lt;/b&gt; ICRM / CRC (Independent Compliance Risk Management)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lifecycle:&lt;/b&gt; Production&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Business Criticality:&lt;/b&gt; MEDIUM&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Data Classification:&lt;/b&gt; Internal&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Data Privacy:&lt;/b&gt; Yes — Internal PII&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hosting Model:&lt;/b&gt; Internal-CTI (On-Premise + Container)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Platform:&lt;/b&gt; Citi Risk and Controls (CRC)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Assessment Frequency:&lt;/b&gt; Annual (Nov – Q1 following year)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Data Date (2025 cycle):&lt;/b&gt; October 13, 2025&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Risk Framework:&lt;/b&gt; GRC Risk Taxonomy (MCA GAU-SAU structure — 2025 target state)&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Downstream Sole Registered:&lt;/b&gt; GCB Xceptor RPA (CSI-173877)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Acronyms:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;CRA — Compliance Risk Assessment&lt;br&gt;ICRM — Independent Compliance Risk Management&lt;br&gt;MCA — Manager&#39;s Control Assessment&lt;br&gt;GAU — Global Assessment Unit  |  SAU — Service Assessment Unit&lt;br&gt;IR — Inherent Risk  |  CE — Control Environment  |  RR — Residual Risk&lt;br&gt;CIA — Compliance Independent Assessment&lt;br&gt;BRCC — Business Risk and Control Committee&lt;br&gt;ICAPS — Integrated Corrective Action Plan System&lt;br&gt;CDE — Compliance Data Engine  |  BAW — Business Activity Warehouse" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=0;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;" parent="meta_bg" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="8" y="26" width="590" height="316" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
